'''Ellie Henry''' is the mother of [[Scott Henry]], who was hospitalized after a tunnel collapse.

==History==
When her son, Scott, was injured in a tunnel collapse while on a trip for a college visit, Ellie and her husband, [[Rob Henry|Rob]], came out to Seattle to see him after his surgery.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
She is married to [[Rob Henry]]. They have a son together, Scott.

===Familial===
Ellie has a son, Scott, who was injured during a college visit when a tunnel collapsed.
